metadata.name: Pillar of Euraphaessa
metadata.description:
Title: Pillar of Euraphaessa 

Chapter: [Chapter I. - The Calm Before](https://omnimorphs.medium.com/the-calm-before-chapter-i-8b5d29313a01) 

Artist: [Daniel Taylor](https://twitter.com/DanielTaylorArt)

The council waits at the center of the city, encircling a great structure, known as the “Pillar of Euraphaessa”. It towers into the sky, a dark obelisk covered in thin fractures of iridescent colour. A structure designed to focus and extend the consciousness of its user.
